《'''不標準情人'''》（{{朝|諺=남자가 사랑할 때|漢=男子가 사랑할 때}}）是一部於2014年上映的韓國[[爱情片|愛情電影]]。電影講述了一個身患絕症的黑幫老大第一次也是最後一次墜入愛河的故事<ref>{{cite web|last=Song|first=Soon-jin|title=4 Big Releases March Into Theaters for Korean New Year|url=http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/features.jsp?seq=236&mode=FEATURES_VIEW|work=Korean Film Council|accessdate=2014-02-16|date=6 January 2014|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525021049/http://www.koreanfilm.or.kr/jsp/news/features.jsp?seq=236&mode=FEATURES_VIEW}}</ref>。由黃晸玟和韓惠軫主演<ref>{{cite web|last=Ji|first=Yong-jin|title=Charming and Addictive Korean Films: Impactful melodrama that will move audiences (When a Man Is in Love)|url=http://koreanfilm.or.kr/webzine/sub/feature.jsp?mode=A_VIEW&wbSeq=100|work=Korean Cinema Today|accessdate=2014-02-16|date=2013-04-25|archive-date=2019-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226045821/http://koreanfilm.or.kr/webzine/sub/feature.jsp?mode=A_VIEW&wbSeq=100}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Jung|first=Ji-won|title=Hwang Jung-min, a man in love with acting|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=2984911|work=韓國中央日報|accessdate=2014-02-16|date=2014-02-14|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724035711/https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=2984911}}</ref>。2021年被臺灣翻拍電影《[[當男人戀愛時_(2021年電影)|當男人戀愛時]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/04/man-in-love-taiwan-movie-box-office-sony-1234743131/|title=Taiwan Falls For ‘Man In Love’; Sony-Distributed Drama Is Top Local Release Of Pandemic Era|publisher=Deadline|access-date=2021-07-30|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426195153/https://deadline.com/2021/04/man-in-love-taiwan-movie-box-office-sony-1234743131/}}</ref>，同年10月29日中國大陸推出翻拍版《東北戀哥》<ref>{{cite news |author1=鍾雨璉 |title=陸版《當男人戀愛時》男主角曝光！「頭鑽窗口」經典畫面全拷貝 |url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/2107948 |accessdate=2021-11-01 |work=ETtoday |date=2021-10-23 |archive-date=2021-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206205530/https://star.ettoday.net/news/2107948 }}</ref>。

